# Redarbor Jobs
---

## Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Expo SDK 52 | Mobile framework |
| React Native 0.76 | UI layer |
| TypeScript | Type safety |
| Zustand | Global state management |
| Expo Router | File-based navigation |
| NativeWind | Tailwind CSS for React Native |
| AsyncStorage | Favorites persistence |
| React Native WebView | HTML job descriptions |
| FlashList | Performant job lists |
| Expo Sharing | Share jobs natively |

---

## Features

### 📋 Job Listings
- List of remote jobs with company logo, title, company name, location and publication date
- Text search by title and company name
- Filter by category (using `/categories` endpoint)
- Filter by job type (full-time, contract, etc.)
- Visual indicator for saved favorites
- Pull-to-refresh
- Visual states: loading, error, empty results

### 🔍 Job Detail
- Full company and position information
- Salary (when available)
- Full HTML job description rendered natively
- Save / remove from favorites
- Apply to job (opens external URL)
- Share job natively

### ❤️ Favorites
- Persisted across app restarts using AsyncStorage
- Remove jobs from favorites
- Navigate to job detail from favorites
- Empty state when no favorites saved

---

## Project Structure

```
redarbor-jobs/
├── app/
│   ├── (tabs)/
│   │   ├── _layout.tsx       # Tab navigator
│   │   ├── index.tsx         # Job listings screen
│   │   └── favorites.tsx     # Favorites screen
│   ├── job/
│   │   └── [id].tsx          # Job detail screen
│   └── _layout.tsx           # Root stack layout
├── src/
│   ├── api/
│   │   └── remotive.ts       # Remotive API client
│   ├── types/
│   │   └── job.ts            # TypeScript interfaces
│   ├── store/
│   │   ├── useJobsStore.ts   # Jobs + filters state (Zustand)
│   │   └── useFavoritesStore.ts # Favorites + persistence (Zustand)
│   ├── hooks/
│   │   ├── useJobs.ts        # Jobs fetching hook
│   │   └── useCategories.ts  # Categories fetching hook
│   └── components/
│       ├── JobCard.tsx        # Job list item
│       ├── SearchBar.tsx      # Search input
│       ├── FilterBar.tsx      # Category and type filters
│       ├── FavoriteButton.tsx # Save/unsave button
│       ├── EmptyState.tsx     # Empty results UI
│       ├── LoadingState.tsx   # Loading skeleton UI
│       └── ErrorState.tsx     # Error UI with retry
├── app.json
├── babel.config.js
├── tailwind.config.js
└── tsconfig.json
```

